dejen de amar?

306
00:11:44,966 --> 00:11:47,216
Invítalos a vivir con nosotros.

307
00:11:51,222 --> 00:11:53,172
Amigo, Bernadette amará ésto.

308
00:11:53,174 --> 00:11:55,058
